Various ways for tying cows:-Sailors knot; Running knot (around the horns), tinker's knot; lock knot; bow knot;



A goat is put into the cowhouse to bring luck.A horseshoe is put over the door of the cowhouse.A bit of palm that would be left after palm Sunday.The cover (what is around the foal when it is born) of a foal to put over the horses in the stable.If a robin went into the cabin it is a sign of good luck.If honey bees make a hive in the wall of the cabin it is the sign of bad luck.
